        <p>None</p>
    </div>
    
    <div type="definition">
        <!-- PREMIS Definition -->
        <p>The aspect, facet, or attribute of an object which is being recorded as a
            significant property.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div type="rationale">
        <!-- PREMIS Rationale -->
        <p>Repositories may choose to describe significant properties based on a
            particular aspect or attribute of an object.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div type="usagenotes">
        <!-- PREMIS Usage notes -->
        <p>This semantic unit is optional and may be used as part of a facet:detail
            pair with <bold>significantPropertiesValue.</bold></p>
    </div>
    
